## STREAK FIX

### Implemented

Normal expiry:

```js
misses++;
missEl.textContent=misses;
```

Purpality expiry:

```js
misses++;
missEl.textContent=misses;
```

### Removed

```js
combo=1;
comboEl.textContent='×1';
```

### Result

| Event             | Combo       |
| ----------------- | ----------- |
| Normal expires    | Preserved   |
| Purpality expires | Preserved   |
| Noise expires     | Preserved   |
| Noise hit         | Reset to ×1 |

This was the primary unfinished task from the original handover.

